cs.SY, cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.MA, cs.IT 

The paper deals with feedback control and coordination over wireless multi-hop networks, which involves topics related to control systems (cs.SY), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), robotics (cs.RO), machine learning (cs.MA), and information theory (cs.IT). However, since the focus is on control design and stability analysis, cs.SY is the most likely category.
